Privacy Policy for Sanzy

Last Updated: December 9, 2024

At Sanzy, accessible from https://t.me/reminiapp_bot, one of our main priorities is the privacy of our users. This Privacy Policy document contains types of information that is collected and recorded by Sanzy and how we use it.

1. Information We Collect

When you use our services, we may collect the following types of personal information:

Telegram Information: Your Telegram username, messages, and media (photos, videos, etc.) shared with us.

User Interaction: Information about how you interact with our services, such as commands sent to our bot, images sent for processing, and usage statistics.

Technical Information: Information about your device or browser (IP address, browser type, operating system, and other technical data).


2. How We Use Your Information

We use the information we collect in the following ways:

To process requests and actions based on your input (such as image processing or getting links).

To improve our services and offer a better user experience.

To communicate with you for service-related notifications, updates, or issues.


3. Data Storage

We store data only for the duration required to fulfill your request. For example, images are temporarily stored for processing and are deleted after the action is completed. We do not store or retain personal messages or data for long periods.

4. Data Sharing and Disclosure

We respect your privacy. Your personal information is not shared with any third parties unless required by law or with your explicit consent. We do not sell or rent your data to any third parties.

5. Security

We take reasonable precautions to protect your information from unauthorized access or alteration. However, please be aware that no method of transmission over the internet is 100% secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute security.

6. Third-Party Services

We may use third-party services to process requests (e.g., image background removal, image enhancements). These third-party services may collect and process data. Please refer to their respective privacy policies for more details.

7. Changes to This Privacy Policy

We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any significant changes by updating the "Last Updated" date at the top of this page. By continuing to use our services, you agree to the updated policy.

8. Contact Us

If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please feel free to contact us via Telegram at @sanzy05.
